high_descs: Turn to the left and then right to the brown dresser.
Pick up the remote from the middle of the dresser, directly behind the tissues.
Hold the remote and move a step to the left.
Hold the remote and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Hold a remote and turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the door, then turn right and go to the dresser against the wall.
Pick up the remote behind the box of tissue, on the dresser.
Turn to your left and go to the wall, then turn to the lamp to your right.
Turn on the lamp in the corner.
Hang a right to walk towards the dresser in the corner.
Pick on the remote that is on the dresser.
Turn to face the lamp on the right of the dresser.
Turn on the lamp next to the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Look at a remote under a lit lamp.
